{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the diagnosis efficacy, \"Tongyi Qianwen\" achieved an accuracy of 61.11% (95% CI:60.84%-61.29), with a sensitivity of 91.67% (95% CI:91.37%-91.96%) and a specificity of 47.95% (95% CI:47.65%-48.25%).",
    "\"Lingyi Zhihui\" demonstrated an accuracy of 76.40% (95% CI:76.17%-76.63%), with a sensitivity of 90.99% (95% CI:90.67%-91.31%) and a specificity of 70.15% (95% CI:69.85%-70.44%).",
    "The human experts were asked to perform the diagnostic test based on the same content fed to LLMs.",
    "A total of 8 physicians completed this task.",
    "Human experts achieved a mean accuracy of 86.37% (95% CI:86.18%-86.55%), a sensitivity of 79.62% (95% CI:79.20%-80.04%), and a specificity of 89.26%(95% CI:89.06%-89.46%)(Table 1)."
  ]
}